      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through an M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanical highlights include a recent preventative rod bearing service and updated throttle actuators, addressing the platform's primary maintenance concerns. The chassis retains its factory-tuned kinematics with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adjustable compression and rebound cycles. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its 'good' status, the internal combustion components and VANOS system exhibit perfect timing synchronization and high-pressure oil delivery.",
